<page>
	
	<topic>DLG_MAINT Maintenance Component</topic>
<description>Application administrators use the DLG_MAINT component to pack or reindex tables on the ASWPACKREINDEX.A5W page.. 
</description>	
<sections>
	<section>
		<title>Discussion</title>
		<description>The DLG_MAINT component shows a list of DBF tables that can be packed or reindexed. If a selected operation can not be completed because a table is open, a view will display showing a list of all tables that could not be updated.
</description>
